---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="pt-32 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto pb-20">
    <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl liquid-glass">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-4">
        I'm Den, a <span class="text-white">19-year-old</span> developer based in <span class="text-white">Chennai, India</span>. I'm drawn to the layer where software meets the metal—the shells, the interpreters, and the event loops that quietly power everything else.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-4">
        I write mostly <span class="text-white">Go</span> and I'm comfortable in the <span class='text-white'>shell</span> as both a user and a builder. I'm currently deepening my understanding of <span class="text-white">Rust</span> as a natural extension of my systems work. When a project calls for it, I'll reach for the right framework to get the job done, but my curiosity always pulls me back toward understanding what's happening underneath.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-4">
        Lately, I've been spending time on <span class="text-white">AI and machine learning</span>, not just using models, but building them from scratch to understand how they actually learn. It's a different kind of problem-solving, and I'm enjoying the shift in perspective.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-4">
        I value code that is clear, fast, and honest. I believe in shipping things that work, documenting what matters, and learning in public along the way.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white/90">Education</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white">B.Tech in Computer Science</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/50">VIT Chennai, India</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Jul 2024 - Aug 2028</p>
          </li>
          <li class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white">BS in Data Science</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/50">IIT Madras</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Jul 2024 - Aug 2028</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-white/90">
          Activities & Leadership
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white">GDG on Campus | VIT Chennai</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Data Scientist</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Sep 2025 - Present</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white">IEEE Computer Society - VITC</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Technical Team Member</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Aug 2025 - Apr 2026</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-2 border-white/20 pl-4">
            <h3 class="font-medium text-white">CodeChef VIT-Chennai Chapter</h3>
            <div class="mt-1 space-y-3">
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
                  Social Media and Content Writing Lead
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Jun 2025 - Apr 2026</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Web Development Team Member</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Feb 2025 - Aug 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white/70">
                  Social Media and Content Writing Specialist
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Jan 2025 - Jun 2025</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
